content: <articles>    <article xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink/">   <front>     <article-meta>       <title-group>         <article-title>Updating the Dartmouth stellar evolution model grid: Pre-main-sequence models & magnetic fields</article-title>       </title-group>       <contrib-group>         <contrib contrib-type="author">           <name>             <surname>Chaboyer</surname>             <given-names>Brian</given-names>           </name>           <aff>             <institution>Dartmouth College</institution>           </aff>         </contrib>         <contrib contrib-type="author">           <name>             <surname>Jones</surname>             <given-names>Jaquille</given-names>           </name>           <aff>             <institution>Dartmouth College</institution>           </aff>         </contrib>         <contrib contrib-type="author">           <name>             <surname>Feiden</surname>             <given-names>Gregory</given-names>           </name>           <aff>             <institution>Uppsala University</institution>           </aff>         </contrib>       </contrib-group>       <pub-date pub-type="pub">         <year>2014</year>       </pub-date>       <self-uri xlink:href="http://zenodo.org/record/10649"/>       <self-uri xlink:href="http://www.coolstars18.net"/>       <self-uri xlink:href="https://zenodo.org/record/10649/files/poster_CS18_model_grid.pdf"/>       <self-uri xlink:href="https://zenodo.org/record/10649/files/poster_CS18_model_grid.png?subformat=icon-90"/>     </article-meta>     <abstract><p>Poster from The 18th Workshop on Cool Stars, Stellar Systems, and the Sun on updating the Dartmouth stellar evolution model grid.
